{"tid":2461662,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐，法式燉牛肉","createTime":"2021-03-25T13:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T21:32:30.000Z","uid":93141,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"408125514c3295638a48533e1ab934b326688c3e","tid":2461662,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXHa1H4FePeV4GyC719mF7gXeMm5uUt8CDYF2pRaP7PNy?filename=5nMtBqt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nMtBqt.jpg&h=3b6440e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前菜：Chicken Liver P&acirc;t&eacute;<br />\n鴨油炒香洋蔥絲，炒到焦糖化<br />\n倒出洋蔥炒雞肝，用大火快炒到外表金黃<br />\n加干邑，Flamb&eacute; <br />\n酒燒完後，加辣椒粉，紅酒醋，洋蔥略煮，入攪拌機打勻，搞掂<br />\n<br />\n前菜：Salmon tartare<br />\n三文魚先切條，再切粒，最後切碎<br />\n切碎蔥，紅洋蔥，青瓜，酸豆，橄欖，刁草，刨檸檬皮<br />\n用胡椒鹽橄欖油檸檬汁調味後攪勻，搞掂<br />\n<br />\n主菜：Pot Au Feu<br />\n先準備bouquet garni，將迷迭香，百里香，月桂葉，香芹莖，西芹綁成一卷<br />\n用油爆牛肉表面至金黃<br />\n加清雞湯蓋過牛肉，加入插上丁香既對切洋蔥，加入bouquet garni，煮三個半鐘<br />\n準備鍾意既蔬菜，再煮半個鐘<br />\n取出食材後過濾油脂，搞掂<br />\n<br />\n甜品: 我"},{"pid":"48a9c93d1096728fe0f862ffb380cb8ae882cfda","tid":2461662,"uid":318204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"樓豬自己煮嘅？"},{"pid":"141833dc0a5204959a5d59ce607283bf2c243b0a","tid":2461662,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"哇好高級 好耐無見過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d36fadeeb322abaa2bfeeebbd4f99bff4b312b","tid":2461662,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a9c93d1096728fe0f862ffb380cb8ae882cfda","tid":2461662,"uid":318204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"樓豬自己煮嘅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"緊係<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e612b5c11c5b633eb3fd5a5dd8bb2fdbf84ec25a","tid":2461662,"uid":369192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1